    "On the other hand, the extensive collinearity of its CC and EE subgenomes with those of its Robusta and Eugenioides progenitors is likely to facilitate introgression of interesting traits from these species, as already happened historically in the Timor spontaneous hybrid.",
    "The high-quality genome sequences of the three species provided in this work, together with the identification of the genomic region conferring resistance to coffee leaf rust, constitute a cornerstone for the breeding of novel Arabica varieties with superior adaptability and pathogen resistance.",
